config FDC1004
	bool "Texas Instruments FDC1004 Capacitance-to-Digital Converter"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_TI_FDC1004_ENABLED
	select I2C
	help
	  Enable driver for the TI FDC1004 4-channel, 16-bit capacitance-to-digital
	  converter. Communicates over I2C. Exposes four single-ended measurement
	  channels (CIN1..CIN4) via the Zephyr sensor API using private channel IDs
	  defined in <fdc1004.h>.
